CANON PRINTER MX922 SETUP

Enter Printer Model


Installation of Canon Pixma mx922 wps button

Network Setup for WPS button on canon mx922

  • Make sure the router is ready and programmed correctly.
  • Fit your printer and wall outlet with the power cord.
  • Click the left front button of the printer. Click on the button. Please.
  • The blue light will automatically be illuminated and steady next to the copy press.
  • Click the menu button to continue with the printer and the various on-screen options such as Photo, WiFi Configuration, Web Service, etc.
  • You can see four-way arrow keys on the front right panel of your printer.. Pick the WLAN configuration method by using the keys.
  • Then your router activated by WPS is identified by the printer.
  • Go to the router and find the WPS button now. You should review your router manual to validate the WPS button.
  • On your wifi press on the canon mx922 WPS button. This will trigger the light flashing next to the mx992 WPS button.
  • For the Canon Printer MX922, press the OK button. On your wifi press on the WPS button
  • When the console reveals the “Linked to Gateway” warning. Push Ok.

Computer Installation of Canon Printer MX922

  • The first move is to open a stable web browser, such as Opera and Safari to access Canon’s official Web page. Enter usa.canon.com and you can get to the site of Canon Printers.
  • The search bar can be conveniently found in the center of the page. You just have to type your version, i.e. In printer MX922. Your model number will appear in the list promptly. Tap on Go, pick the printer.
  • All information about the device, such as manuals, printer specs, etc. can be read on this tab.
  • Click on the Drivers & Downloads tab below the name of your product model. You’ll note two separate categories of Recommended and Optional Drivers at the bottom of the list.
  • You must fill in the operating system and the language fields to download the driver. Therefore, making the right decision.
  • Tap on “Select” and then click the Update button under the segment Recommended engine.
  • The file exe or dmg will appear to be downloaded based on the operating system of your computer.
  • Open the Canon Printer MX922 configuration file downloaded to launch. Select Next on the welcoming panel.
  • The choice of place of residence is requested. Tap Next when you’ve picked.
  • Select Next and no drivers will be installed, approve the License Agreement.
  • Pick in the link method screen the “Use Canon printer with wifi LAN connection” button and then click Next.
  • Starting with the Canon Printer MX922. Confirm your model number and press Next until found.
  • You will update the app right now, press Complete.

How do you execute the WPS button on the access point canon printer mx922 test process?

  • Go to Windows for Hardware and Sound and select “System and printer view.” In Mac, choose Apple menu choices, then Print & Fax, and select the Print tab.
  • On the left side of the printer, a green checkmark emerged. Right-click it to choose the printer’s settings.
  • Remove your printer’s paper tray, move the paper directions, and place a pile of paper neatly.
  • Change the paper guides on the side, put the paper tray on the printer again. Open the printer’s outer cover and extend the output layer to the page.
  • Click on the test page button on the printer properties tab of your machine. The Canon Printer MX922 setup is done. This page is printed.

These are the complete steps to set up the canon Pixma mx922 WPS button.
